<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title || 'MudaEdu — Em manutenção' %></title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --dark-lilac: #5B35D9;
            --lilac: #7060F0;
            --gold: #d97706;
            --ink: #1e293b;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: var(--ink);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(112, 96, 240, 0.12), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.10), transparent 35%),
                linear-gradient(160deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            width: min(560px, 100%);
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--dark-lilac);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            margin: 0 auto 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(91, 53, 217, 0.12), rgba(112, 96, 240, 0.08));
            color: var(--dark-lilac);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 1.65rem;
            color: var(--dark-lilac);
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        .status-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #fff7ed;
            color: #9a3412;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .status-pill i {
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .details {
            text-align: left;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .details li {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .details li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .brand {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .brand .brand-muda { color: #0A0A0A; }
        .brand .brand-edu { color: #20B0F0; }
        .brand .brand-suffix { color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 600; margin-left: 0.35em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="maintenance-card" role="main" aria-labelledby="maintenance-title">
        <div class="maintenance-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="status-pill">
            <i class="fas fa-circle-notch fa-spin"></i>
            Em manutenção
        </div>

        <h1 id="maintenance-title">MudaEdu temporariamente indisponível</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            Estamos realizando uma manutenção programada neste ambiente.
            O acesso será restabelecido em breve.
        </p>

        <ul class="details">
            <li><strong>O que está acontecendo:</strong> manutenção técnica da plataforma.</li>
            <li><strong>Quando voltamos:</strong> assim que a manutenção for concluída pela equipe LeAction.</li>
            <li><strong>Precisa de suporte?</strong> Entre em contato com o administrador do projeto.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="brand brand-on-light"><span class="brand-muda">Muda</span><span class="brand-edu">Edu</span><span class="brand-suffix">· LeAction System</span></div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
